result.name: 家家樂魚蛋麵

reviews.text:
I'm so happy I found this place near my hotel. One of the things I crave the most is soup noodles and congee and this place delivers! With the number of small traditional congee shops shutting, it makes me sad every time I visit HK when I find it more and more difficult to find one. 
My fav preserved egg and lean meat congee in the photos but they do a plethora of other types. Best to just go in a shout out what you want since they mix and match anything and everything.
The exact price they would charge up in Kowloon for the locals. 30hkd for congee and up, and same for your basic wonton noodle soup and up!
A place to get cheap eats, it was very tight and had limited seating.
Good taste and clean
The wonton noodle taste good, but the seating space is too small.

Fantastic food for very reasonable prices considering it is located in Causeway Bay. I particularly liked the congee which was starchy and thick, typically what one would only find in more expensive restaurants.

reviews.text: 有粥 有飯 有嘢飲 例如奶茶咖啡 個牛腩牛筋ok嘅 主打豬手 牛腩 價錢貴咗少少 普通一碗麵35蚊起 飯就43蚊起 上湯係正宗大地魚做嘅 不過湯底都係唔夠味 奶茶咖啡機本就普通通 本身個老闆都喺附近開茶餐廳 蛋奶茶仍然係未及水準 所以點解有很多人 去麥奀記去池記 麥文記 事關佢哋嘅湯底 麵條 係真係好食啲
價廉物美，粥麵水準非常，高尤其是豬手及牛腩每次必食。

I'm so happy I found this place near my hotel. One of the things I crave the most is soup noodles and congee and this place delivers! With the number of small traditional congee shops shutting, it makes me sad every time I visit HK when I find it more and more difficult to find one. 
My fav preserved egg and lean meat congee in the photos but they do a plethora of other types. Best to just go in a shout out what you want since they mix and match anything and everything.
The exact price they would charge up in Kowloon for the locals. 30hkd for congee and up, and same for your basic wonton noodle soup and up!
價錢便宜食物美味，牛腩和豬手煮得很腍滑。

靠近中央圖書館附近既小食店，經濟又實惠，二十幾元一碗既麵食質量及味道都是棒棒的，招呼周到，店員友善，最出名既南乳豬手麵/米粉，水餃，牛腩及雲吞，其它食物，毫不遜色，本人最喜愛就是浸住麵食既湯，少鹽，淡淡的味道合到好處，並無一般食店的多鹽及極濃的味道。地方細小，座位郤不少，故會位與位之間稍微狹窄，但仍屬可接受範圍。
位置：銅鑼灣道一號，聖保祿醫院斜對面。
極力推薦
